* Get-IsWinServerWeb.ps1 - Is this a Windows Server Web Server edition? - RETURNS: True or False
* Get-IsWinWorkstation.ps1 - Is this a Windows Workstation (not server)? - RETURNS: True or False
* Get-PendingReboot.ps1 - Is the computer pending a reboot? - RETURNS: True or False
* Get-WinName.ps1 - Windows version name  - RETURNS: a string
* Get-WinVerBuild.ps1 - Windows version build #? - RETURNS: the Windows build #
* Get-WinVerMajor.ps1 - Windows major version - RETURNS: Windows major version (i.e. 7/8/10)
